#

Pesto Chicken Burger

30 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyQuickComfort Food

Description

Juicy chicken burger topped with fresh pesto and melted cheese, served on a toasted bun with crisp lettuce and tomato.

Ingredients

  • ground chicken: 1 pound
  • burger buns: 4
  • pesto sauce: 1/4 cup
  • mozzarella cheese: 4 slices
  • lettuce: 4 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
